564
00:40:18,917 --> 00:40:21,083
"Para todo o sempre."

565
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:36,382
<i>Desculpe, eu...</i>

566
00:40:37,469 --> 00:40:40,025
<i>Não devia ter contado
